#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:2
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "Frequently Asked Questions"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:9
msgid "如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？"
msgstr "How to disable GPU power saving mode to avoid slow inference?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:11
msgid ""
"在某些设备上，如果连续使用模型推理，执行速度非常快（例如 10 毫秒以内）；但如果两个推理调用之间的间隔较长（例如超过 5 "
"秒），则可能出现执行时间大幅变慢的情况（例如变成 100 毫秒以上 然后之后回到10ms以内）。"
msgstr ""
"On some machines, back-to-back model inference is very fast (under 10 ms), "
"but when two inference calls are spaced apart (more than ~5 seconds), the "
"second call can be significantly slower (over 100 ms) before returning to "
"the normal ~10 ms."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:13
msgid "这是由于 GPU 进入低功耗状态导致的性能下降问题。"
msgstr ""
"The slowdown comes from the GPU dropping into a low-power state between "
"calls."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:15
msgid "为了保证您的设备始终以高性能运行，建议您进行以下设置："
msgstr ""
"To keep the machine running at full performance, apply these settings:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:19
msgid "在 NVIDIA 控制面板中设置："
msgstr "In the NVIDIA Control Panel:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:18
msgid "打开 NVIDIA Control Panel → Manage 3D Settings。"
msgstr "Open **NVIDIA Control Panel → Manage 3D Settings**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:19
msgid "找到 Power management mode，设置为 Prefer maximum performance。"
msgstr ""
"Find **Power management mode** and set it to **Prefer maximum performance**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:23
msgid "在系统电源管理中设置："
msgstr "In Windows Power Options:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:22
msgid "打开 控制面板 → 电源选项。"
msgstr "Open **Control Panel → Power Options**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:23
msgid "选择 高性能 电源计划。"
msgstr "Pick the **High performance** plan."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:25
msgid "设置示例如下图所示："
msgstr "Example settings are shown below:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:-1
msgid "GPU 设置示例"
msgstr "GPU settings example"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:-1
msgid "控制面板电源选项"
msgstr "Control Panel — Power Options"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:36
msgid "如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？"
msgstr "How to enable hardware acceleration in the browser to avoid lag?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:38
msgid "在编程一个元件数量较多的 PCB 模板时，浏览器可能会出现卡顿现象。建议开启浏览器的硬件加速功能以提升性能。"
msgstr ""
"Programming a PCB template with many components can make the browser "
"stutter. Enable browser hardware acceleration for a smoother experience."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:46
msgid "启用硬件加速（Edge）："
msgstr "Enable hardware acceleration in Edge:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:41
msgid "打开 Microsoft Edge"
msgstr "Open Microsoft Edge."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:42
msgid "点击右上角“...” → “设置”"
msgstr "Click the *…* menu at the top right → **Settings**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:43
msgid "左侧选择“系统和性能”"
msgstr "Pick **System and performance** on the left."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:44
msgid "点击 “系统”"
msgstr "Click **System**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:45
msgid "找到“在可用时使用硬件加速”并勾选启用"
msgstr "Find **Use hardware acceleration when available** and turn it on."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:46
msgid "若提示“重新启动”，点击以生效"
msgstr "Click **Restart** when prompted so the change takes effect."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:48
msgid "确保您的显卡驱动程序是最新的。"
msgstr "Make sure the graphics driver is up to date."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:-1
msgid "Edge 浏览器硬件加速设置示例"
msgstr "Edge hardware acceleration — example"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:64
msgid "自动编程没有 CAD 可以吗？"
msgstr "Can Auto-Programming run without CAD?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:66
msgid "可以。未提供 CAD 时，系统会："
msgstr "Yes. Without CAD, the system:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:68
msgid "仅基于图像/AI 识别结果生成初始元件框集合。"
msgstr "Generates the initial component-box set from vision and AI alone."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:69
msgid "不能自动补充料号、封装、丝印映射，需要人工后续补录。"
msgstr ""
"Cannot fill in part numbers, packages, or designators automatically — those "
"need to be entered manually later."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:70
msgid "分组初期只能按“封装（推断/人工）”或“主体外形”进行粗分。"
msgstr ""
"Initial grouping is rough — by inferred / manual package, or by body shape."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:72
msgid ""
"推荐做法： 1. 先执行自动编程获取基础框。 2. 手动补充关键元件的封装与料号（优先高价值器件）。 3. 统一封装命名后，再做参数调优与训练。"
msgstr ""
"Recommended approach: (1) run Auto-Programming to get the baseline boxes; "
"(2) fill in package and part number on the key components (high-value "
"first); (3) standardize the package names, then tune parameters and train."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:78
msgid "元件录入时只有封装，没有料号可以吗？"
msgstr "Can I enter components with only the package, no part number?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:80
msgid "可以。系统会先按封装分组："
msgstr "Yes. The system groups by package first:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:82
msgid "优点：仍可聚合样本、共享封装级参数。"
msgstr ""
"Upside: samples still aggregate and package-level parameters are shared."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:83
msgid "局限：无法区分同封装不同规格（如阻值/容值），统计维度较粗。"
msgstr ""
"Limitation: parts with the same package but different specs (different "
"resistance or capacitance values) can't be distinguished; statistics stay "
"coarse."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:85
msgid "后续补录料号后： * 自动进入封装下的二级料号节点。 * 已有参数继承保留，可再按料号覆盖特化（如亮度阈值）。"
msgstr ""
"Once part numbers are filled in later, the components automatically slot "
"into the second-tier PN node under their package. Existing inherited "
"parameters stay; you can then override at the PN level (for example, a "
"different brightness threshold)."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:90
msgid "某一个元件频繁误检，是否应单独脱离分组？"
msgstr ""
"A single component fires false positives constantly — should I detach it "
"from its group?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:92
msgid ""
"排查顺序建议： 1. 确认其标注是否正确（主体 / 焊料 / 引脚框是否偏移）。 2. 对比同封装其它样本是否共有问题：若多数异常 → "
"说明封装级参数需调整。 3. 仅该件异常 → 检查是否器件瑕疵 / 光照阴影 / 翘脚。"
msgstr ""
"Diagnose in this order: (1) verify the annotations are correct (body / "
"solder / lead boxes not shifted); (2) compare against other samples of the "
"same package — if many show the issue, the package-level parameters need "
"tuning; (3) if only this one shows it, look for a part defect, lighting "
"shadow, or lifted lead."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:97
msgid ""
"如果确认该元件与组内模式差异较大（颜色、焊料成形、几何高度）： * 可临时关闭“Link Package / Link PN”脱离继承，单独调整。 * "
"若差异具有系统性（整批次都不同），应新建料号；若几何本质不同，应新建封装。"
msgstr ""
"If the component genuinely differs from the rest of the group (color, solder"
" shape, geometric height): turn off **Link Package / Link PN** temporarily "
"and tune it independently. If the difference is systemic (the whole batch "
"differs), create a new PN; if the geometry differs fundamentally, create a "
"new package."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:101
msgid "注意：脱离分组后参数修改不会再反馈到组内。"
msgstr ""
"Note: once a component is unlinked, its parameter changes no longer flow "
"back into the group."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:104
msgid "修改封装参数后需重新训练吗？"
msgstr "Do I need to retrain after changing package parameters?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:106
msgid "分情况："
msgstr "It depends:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:108
msgid "纯检测参数阈值（阈值、面积、距离、比率等）调整：无需重新训练，保存后即时生效。"
msgstr ""
"Adjusting only the inspection thresholds (threshold, area, distance, ratio):"
" no retraining — the change takes effect on save."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:109
msgid "重绘/增删检测框（主体、焊料、引脚掩膜）导致样本几何变化：需要重新训练，以更新特征表示。"
msgstr ""
"Redrawing or adding / removing inspection boxes (body, solder, lead-mask) "
"changes sample geometry: retrain so the feature representation is updated."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:110
msgid "批量合并/拆分组（封装或料号）后：若仅分组结构变化通常无需训练；若引入了大量新增样本，建议增量再训练一次提升稳定性。"
msgstr ""
"Bulk merging / splitting groups (by package or PN): if only the grouping "
"structure changed, retraining is usually unnecessary; if a large batch of "
"new samples was pulled in, run an incremental retrain for stability."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:114
msgid "如何在元件里新增检测项？"
msgstr "How do I add a new inspection item to a component?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:116
msgid "要在元件中新增检测项（ROI），请按以下步骤操作："
msgstr "To add a new inspection item (ROI) to a component:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:118
msgid "在模板编辑器中，选中目标元件（已分组）。"
msgstr ""
"In the Template Editor, select the target component (must be grouped)."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:119
msgid "在右侧属性栏找到”在组中添加 ROI”按钮。"
msgstr ""
"In the property panel on the right, find the **Add ROI to group** button."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:120
msgid "点击后，进入 ROI 编辑模式，可在图像上框选新的检测区域。"
msgstr ""
"Click it to enter ROI-editing mode and draw the new inspection region on the"
" image."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:121
msgid "添加您需要的 ROI 类型（如焊料、引脚、文本、条码等）"
msgstr "Add the ROI type you need — solder, lead, text, barcode, and so on."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:122
msgid "然后保存并退出即可。"
msgstr "Save and exit."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:125
msgid "“以演示模式运行”是什么？"
msgstr "What is *Run in demo mode*?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:127
msgid "**以演示模式运行** 是新建检测任务弹窗中的一个勾选项。勾选后："
msgstr ""
"**Run in demo mode** is a checkbox on the New Inspection Task dialog. When "
"checked:"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:129
msgid "检测任务自动运行，无需手动触发。"
msgstr "The inspection task runs automatically — no manual trigger needed."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:130
msgid "检测到缺陷时，系统在复检页面停留约 7 秒，随后自动返回实时检测页面并继续。"
msgstr ""
"When a defect is detected, the system pauses on the Review page for about 7 "
"seconds, then returns to Live and continues."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:131
msgid "按 ``Esc`` 可随时退出演示模式。"
msgstr "Press ``Esc`` to exit demo mode at any time."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:132
msgid "演示模式下无法通过按钮手动触发检测。"
msgstr "Manual button triggers are disabled in demo mode."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:134
msgid "详情请参见 :doc:`../complete_user_guide/inspection/index` 中的”新建检测任务”一节。"
msgstr ""
"For the full reference, see the *Starting a new inspection task* section in "
":doc:`../complete_user_guide/inspection/index`."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:137
msgid "实时检测页面的”整板 / 子板”直通率切换是什么含义？"
msgstr "What does the *Board / Sub-board* FPY toggle on the Live page mean?"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:139
msgid "实时检测页面（Live）右侧统计面板上方提供 **整板 / 子板** 切换控件，用于选择直通率（FPY）的统计口径："
msgstr ""
"Above the statistics panel on the Live page, a **Board / Sub-board** toggle "
"picks the scope for First Pass Yield (FPY):"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:141
msgid "**整板**：以整块 PCB 为单位计算直通率（合格板数 / 已检测板数），标签显示 **主板直通率**。"
msgstr ""
"**Board**: FPY is computed per whole PCB (passed boards / inspected boards);"
" the label reads **Board FPY**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:142
msgid "**子板**：以子板为单位计算，仅适用于拼板产品，标签显示 **子板直通率**；非拼板产品显示 **N/A**。"
msgstr ""
"**Sub-board**: computed per sub-board, available only for panel products; "
"the label reads **Sub-board FPY**. Non-panel products show **N/A**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:144
msgid ""
"该设置会持久化保存，页面刷新后仍保留。子板判废逻辑（比例模式 / 坏板标记模式）在产品设置的 **检测设置** 子标签中配置，详情请参见 "
":ref:`检测设置（子板判废逻辑）`。"
msgstr ""
"The setting persists across page reloads. The sub-board verdict logic (ratio"
" mode / badmark mode) is configured under the **Inspection Settings** sub-"
"tab in the product Recipe; see :ref:`检测设置（子板判废逻辑）`."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:147
msgid "软件升级与安装"
msgstr "Software upgrade and installation"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:150
msgid "升级后软件无法启动或拍不了照片"
msgstr "After an upgrade the software won't start or can't capture"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:152
msgid "升级前请先 **重启电脑**，避免后台残留进程导致旧版本卸载不干净。"
msgstr ""
"Before upgrading, **restart the PC** so the old version's background "
"processes don't leave the install half-removed."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:154
msgid "重启电脑。"
msgstr "Restart the PC."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:155
msgid "卸载旧软件（使用安装目录下的 ``unins000.exe``）。"
msgstr ""
"Uninstall the old version (use ``unins000.exe`` in the install directory)."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:156
msgid "安装新版本。"
msgstr "Install the new version."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:157
msgid "参考随版本发布的更新说明文档完成升级后的额外操作（如校准、配置迁移等）。"
msgstr ""
"Follow the release notes that ship with the new version for any post-upgrade"
" steps — calibration, configuration migration, and so on."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:160
msgid "更新软件后第一次启动很慢"
msgstr "First boot after a software update is slow"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:162
msgid "i7-8 代工控机上首次启动大约需要 **2.5 分钟** 属正常现象；第二次及以后启动会显著加快。等待启动完成即可。"
msgstr ""
"On an 8th-gen i7 IPC, a first boot taking about **2.5 minutes** is normal; "
"subsequent boots are noticeably faster. Just wait for it to finish."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:165
msgid "新版本功能不显示 / 设置里看不到"
msgstr "New features don't show / are missing from Settings"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:167
msgid "浏览器缓存可能未刷新。按 ``Ctrl + R`` 或 ``Ctrl + Shift + R`` 强制刷新浏览器，让最新的前端代码加载进来。"
msgstr ""
"The browser cache may be stale. Hard-refresh with ``Ctrl + R`` or ``Ctrl + "
"Shift + R`` so the latest frontend code loads."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:168
msgid "确认实际安装的软件版本正确（**设置 → 系统设置 → 关于** 页面查看版本号）。"
msgstr ""
"Confirm the actually-installed software version under **Settings → System "
"Settings → About**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:171
msgid "授权 / 加密狗过期，软件无法使用"
msgstr "Licence / dongle expired — software won't run"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:173
msgid "检查加密狗是否插好、USB 接口是否松动。"
msgstr "Check that the dongle is firmly seated and the USB port is not loose."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:174
msgid "在 **设置 → 系统设置 → 关于** 页面查看授权到期日期。"
msgstr ""
"Check the licence expiry date on **Settings → System Settings → About**."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:175
msgid "备用方案：若有备用加密狗，可临时替换使用。"
msgstr "Workaround: if a spare dongle is available, swap it in temporarily."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:178
msgid "软件长时间启动失败（i.e. 与其他软件端口冲突）"
msgstr ""
"Software fails to start for a long time (e.g. port conflict with another "
"app)"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:180
msgid ""
"AOI 软件后端使用 **8000 端口**。若同设备上运行其他占用 8000 端口的程序（如个别音乐 / 通讯软件），AOI 软件无法正常启动。"
msgstr ""
"The AOI backend uses **port 8000**. If another program on the same PC is "
"holding that port (some music or messaging apps do), the AOI software won't "
"start."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:182
msgid "关闭可能占用 8000 端口的其他程序后重新启动 AOI 软件。"
msgstr ""
"Close whichever program might be holding port 8000 and restart the AOI "
"software."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:183
msgid "命令行可通过 ``netstat -ano | findstr :8000`` 查看 8000 端口当前被哪个进程占用。"
msgstr ""
"From the command line, ``netstat -ano | findstr :8000`` shows which process "
"currently owns port 8000."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:187
msgid "软件启动 / 崩溃 / 卡顿"
msgstr "Startup, crashes, and stutters"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:190
msgid "浏览器页面卡顿、不出图"
msgstr "Browser stutters and images don't render"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:192
msgid ""
"按 ``Ctrl + R`` 或 ``Ctrl + Shift + R`` 强制刷新浏览器缓存。如频繁出现，建议同时启用 "
":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？` 中介绍的浏览器硬件加速。"
msgstr ""
"Hard-refresh the browser with ``Ctrl + R`` or ``Ctrl + Shift + R``. If it "
"happens often, also enable browser hardware acceleration as described in "
":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:195
msgid "SSE 报错（后台模块崩溃）"
msgstr "SSE errors (backend module crashed)"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:197
msgid "启动器面板上可看到各后端模块的状态指示。若有模块显示为红色（STOPPED），通常重启软件即可恢复。"
msgstr ""
"The launcher panel displays the status of each backend module. When a module"
" shows red (STOPPED), restarting the software usually brings it back."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:200
msgid "检测记录积累过多导致卡顿"
msgstr "Too many accumulated inspection records cause stutter"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:202
msgid "软件支持自动清理旧检测数据。可在 **设置 → 系统设置 → 系统配置** 中设置保留天数 / 磁盘阈值，过期数据会被自动清理。"
msgstr ""
"The software can clean up old inspection data automatically. Under "
"**Settings → System Settings → System Configuration**, set the retention "
"days and the disk-usage threshold; expired data is cleaned up automatically."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:203
msgid "也可在 **数据分析报告 → 检测结果** 标签页中手动多选并删除指定时间段的检测记录。"
msgstr ""
"You can also manually multi-select and delete records for a given time "
"window on the **Data Analysis Report → Inspection Results** tab."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:207
msgid ""
"**请勿手动删除安装目录下的数据库文件夹**。手动删除可能误删程序数据，导致软件黑屏 / 无法启动。如需清理空间，请使用软件内置的自动 / "
"手动清理功能。"
msgstr ""
"**Do not delete the database folder under the install directory by hand.** "
"Doing so can wipe program state and leave the software unbootable or blank-"
"screen. Free up space through the built-in automatic or manual cleanup "
"features instead."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:210
msgid "软件更新后启动卡在 99%"
msgstr "After an update, startup hangs at 99%"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:212
msgid "重启电脑后重新尝试。"
msgstr "Restart the PC and try again."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:213
msgid "重新运行版本更新。"
msgstr "Re-run the version update."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:214
msgid ""
"检查启动器面板上各模块状态。如果 ``conveyor_server`` "
"显示为红色（STOPPED），可能是设备处于急停状态或硬件初始化失败：先解除急停状态再重启软件；若是硬件初始化失败，请参见硬件相关章节。"
msgstr ""
"Check the per-module status on the launcher panel. If ``conveyor_server`` "
"shows red (STOPPED), the equipment may be in emergency-stop or hardware init"
" may have failed: release the emergency-stop and restart the software; if "
"hardware init is the cause, see the hardware-related section."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:218
msgid "图像质量"
msgstr "Image quality"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:221
msgid "编程拍照时拼接的大图上有重影"
msgstr "Ghosting in the stitched full-board image during programming"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:223
msgid "换一块 PCB 重新拍摄。若依然有重影，说明轨道标定已偏，需要 **重新校准**\\ （相机标定 + 轨道标定）。"
msgstr ""
"Try a different PCB and re-capture. If ghosting persists, the conveyor "
"calibration has drifted and a **re-calibration** is needed (camera "
"calibration + conveyor calibration)."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:224
msgid ""
"若重影是偶发现象，可进入 **设置 → 系统设置 → 捕获模块**，把 **图像拼接配置 → 最大偏移像素 X 与 Y** 调大（例如调到 "
"30）；重启软件后再试。"
msgstr ""
"If the ghosting is intermittent, go to **Settings → System Settings → "
"Capture Module** and increase **Image Stitching Configuration → Max offset "
"pixels X / Y** (try 30); restart the software and try again."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:227
msgid "其他常见问题"
msgstr "Other common issues"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:230
msgid "板子放反时报错处理"
msgstr "Reversed-board handling"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:232
msgid "**板子放反**：在新建检测任务前请再次确认 PCB 放置方向；若使用拼板，注意拼板基准位置。"
msgstr ""
"**Board loaded reversed**: confirm the PCB orientation before starting a new"
" inspection task; on panel products, also check the panel reference "
"position."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:235
msgid "同名程序保留两个版本"
msgstr "Keeping two versions of the same-named program"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:237
msgid "**临时解决**：先 **复制** 旧程序为另一名称，删除旧程序，再导入同名新程序。"
msgstr ""
"**Workaround**: first **duplicate** the old program under a different name, "
"delete the old one, then import the new program with the original name."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:238
msgid "**注意**：删除旧程序后，相关检测记录的图像可能不可见。"
msgstr ""
"**Note**: once the old program is deleted, images for its historical "
"inspection records may no longer be viewable."

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:241
msgid "按料号跳过某些元件不检测"
msgstr "Skip inspection by part number"

#: ../../source/support/faq.rst:243
msgid "在模板编辑器中找到对应料号的元件，关闭它们的所有检测项；或直接使用 :ref:`跳过此元件的检测` 开关进行整体跳过。"
msgstr ""
"In the Template Editor, find the components with that part number and turn "
"off all their inspection items; or use the :ref:`跳过此元件的检测` switch to skip "
"them entirely."

